Package com.barryholroyd.evermore Description

Top-level package for Evermore -- primarily initialization and configuration.

Instance data (e.g., fields) that needs to be retained across device re-configurations is typically stored in static variables (or in data hierarchies referenced by at least one static variable).

1.0
